sequenceDiagram
    participant HP as HTML Parser
    participant Net as Network
    participant CSS as CSS Engine
    participant JS as JS Engine

    HP->>Net: Discover link rel=stylesheet
    HP->>HP: Continue parsing HTML
    Net-->>CSS: CSS bytes arrive
    CSS->>CSS: Tokenize and parse CSS
    HP->>HP: Encounter script tag
    Note over HP: Parser pauses
    HP->>Net: Request script
    Net-->>JS: Script ready
    Note over JS: Blocked: CSSOM not complete
    CSS->>CSS: Finish building CSSOM
    CSS-->>JS: CSSOM ready
    JS->>JS: Execute script
    Note over JS: Can call getComputedStyle()
    JS-->>HP: Script complete
    HP->>HP: Resume parsing
